item.title: E04478
item.description: Manitou MRT1432 Rotary Telescopic Handler, E-rops cab, Perkins 1104T engine with 101HP (74.5kW), EPA Certified, 2 speed hydrostatic transmission, 4WD, 4x4x4 configuration, forks, mechanical quick coupler, extra hydr. spoolvalve, 4 hydraulic stabilizers, max. lift capacity 3.200 Kgs, max. lift height 13.82 Mtr, max. reach 11.63 Mtr, brand new 16.0/70-20 tyres, operating weight 12.340 Kgs, drawbar, CE marked. Machine is driving but electric & hydraulic system need repairs. Inspections are welcome.
